WEBVTT

00:05:28.442 --> 00:05:32.409
putting a glass facade to their shop.

00:05:32.409 --> 00:05:34.706
They had thrown the old shutter

00:05:34.706 --> 00:05:37.698
in the garbage collection place.

00:05:37.698 --> 00:05:41.258
"Why did you throw away the shutters?" I asked him.

00:05:41.258 --> 00:05:46.490
"Well, because the street is safer now," they answered.

00:05:46.490 --> 00:05:52.058
"Safer? Why? They have posted more policemen here?"

00:05:52.058 --> 00:05:54.882
"Come on, man! What policemen?

00:05:54.882 --> 00:05:57.974
You can see it for yourself. There are colors,

00:05:57.974 --> 00:06:03.794
streetlights, new pavement with no potholes,